properties.areaDesc: Waters from San Mateo point to the Mexican Border Extending 30 to 60 nm out including San Clemente Island; Coastal Waters from San Mateo Point to the Mexican Border and out to 30 nm
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 24 at 4:25PM PST by NWS San Diego CA
properties.description:
A shallow marine layer will continue the areas of dense fog
overnight in the coastal waters. Visibility will be less than one
NM at times, with local visibility of a few hundred feet possible.
This will result in hazardous navigation. Conditions will likely
not improve until mid-morning Saturday.

NWSheadline: AREAS OF DENSE FOG OVERNIGHT IN THE COASTAL WATERS
